You will be…

790
00:58:21,748 --> 00:58:22,957
Old lady!

791
00:58:35,053 --> 00:58:37,222
This is the way to my house.

792
00:58:38,014 --> 00:58:39,098
Are you awake now?

793
00:58:40,433 --> 00:58:42,352
Should I put you down?

794
00:58:44,270 --> 00:58:45,730
It's warm.

795
00:58:48,149 --> 00:58:49,901
This reminds me of my dad.

796
00:58:52,153 --> 00:58:54,781
Did he give you piggyback rides often?

797
00:58:55,740 --> 00:58:56,574
Yes.

798
00:58:58,743 --> 00:59:01,412
He would give me a piggyback ride

799
00:59:03,581 --> 00:59:05,416
and sing to me every day.

800
00:59:06,751 --> 00:59:07,794
What song?

801
00:59:14,300 --> 00:59:15,134
What song?

802
00:59:17,637 --> 00:59:19,430
What? Are you asleep?

803
00:59:40,201 --> 00:59:43,788
We should take another walk
around the block.

804
01:00:28,458 --> 01:00:31,085
Hello? Excuse me.

805
01:00:32,879 --> 01:00:33,880
Excuse me.

806
01:00:34,714 --> 01:00:35,882
I have a question.

807
01:00:35,965 --> 01:00:38,301
Gosh, I'm busy right now. What is it?

808
01:01:26,099 --> 01:01:28,643
How long have I walked
with her on my back?

809
01:01:28,726 --> 01:01:29,644
My back hurts.

810
01:01:29,727 --> 01:01:32,438
Bahn Ha-ni, the Lee Hyo-ri of Hosu High?

811
01:01:32,522 --> 01:01:34,899
My Ha-ni?

812
01:01:35,650 --> 01:01:37,777
How do you know
what she looked like in high school?

813
01:01:37,860 --> 01:01:40,405
-Because I've met her then.
-You met my mom?

814
01:01:40,488 --> 01:01:41,447
A contest?

815
01:01:41,531 --> 01:01:43,533
Last year,
the first prize was 5 million won.

816
01:01:43,616 --> 01:01:46,202
-But it's 10 million won this year.
-How much?

817
01:01:46,953 --> 01:01:48,705
Tell me honestly.

818
01:01:48,788 --> 01:01:50,540
What have you gotten yourself into?

